## 1. ALGEBRA

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[79, 195, 234, 212]]<|/det|>
Quadratic Equation

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[116, 225, 381, 244]]<|/det|>
For the equation \(ax^{2} + bx + c = 0\),

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[420, 245, 584, 280]]<|/det|>
\[x = \frac{-b\pm\sqrt{b^{2} - 4ac}}{2a}.\]

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[79, 312, 222, 329]]<|/det|>
Binomial Theorem

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[245, 333, 751, 371]]<|/det|>
\[(a + b)^{n} = a^{n} + \binom{n}{1} a^{n - 1} b + \binom{n}{2} a^{n - 2} b^{2} + \ldots +\binom{n}{r} a^{n - r} b^{r} + \ldots +b^{n},\]

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[116, 381, 500, 415]]<|/det|>
where \(n\) is a positive integer and \(\binom{n}{r} = \frac{n!}{(n-r)!r!}\).
